{"tid":1474441,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全部同我入嚟！光復紅土！唔好去中環 叫人唔好去！","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T03:26:13.000Z","uid":50497,"like":90,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"32ff63e5004c693864ecba545733b076fefb8e61","tid":1474441,"uid":50497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思各位巴絲 點咗你入嚟<br />\n主要想講記得星期六一定要去紅土！<br />\n中環有乜？ 大伏呀！叫人唔好去！<br />\n一定唔可以去<br />\n有個AnimalSaver Hk搞個動保活動<br />\n利申小弟有養貓所以會留意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yb37cKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyb37cKS.jpg&h=a070fb2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身打算去完紅土就去支持吓 點知一起底<br />\n屌你個AS有前科 上年動保活動邀請過葛佩帆<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1198824/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%8C%87%E5%8B%95%E4%BF%9D%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B%E9%81%8E%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E8%81%AF%E5%90%8C%E8%91%9B%E7%8F%AE%E5%B8%86%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E7%99%BC%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1198824%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%2591%259B%25E7%258F%25AE%25E5%25B8%2586%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=b7750ccb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1198824%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%2591%259B%25E7%258F%25AE%25E5%25B8%2586%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C&h=7c2b6a42\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1198824/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%8C%87%E5%8B%95%E4%BF%9D%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B%E9%81%8E%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E8%81%AF%E5%90%8C%E8%91%9B%E7%8F%AE%E5%B8%86%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E7%99%BC%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n大佬呀邀請得呢條葛都知咩料啦<br />\n仲有勁多5毛話動物唔關政治事話照去<br />\n吓？ 依家唔係班狗發癲放TG搞到我隻貓咩 唔關㗎？咁我出嚟做咩？ <br />\n仲有個叫獸醫姐姐個page仲好笑！<br />\n衝出嚟護航 話有建制派就第一時間起身走<br />\n但一講上次葛件事就話「互相利用有咩問題」<br />\n你想紅呀？幫你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQnS8h5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQnS8h5.jpg&h=fb2e959e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLqEOh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLqEOh5.jpg&h=bcd0eb5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n扮乜中立呀？ 冇中立呀！<br />\n真係寧願獸醫界自己搞集會都唔好痴班5毛/藍屍度<br />\n班寵物主人搞都唔係問題 <br />\n但唔好一個二個係中立撚/ 明明係藍又扮中立<br />\n中立難聽過粗口 咁樣同班義工割𥱊有乜分別！<br />\n唔割！ <br />\n玩春袋都唔割！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nsorry第一次打 1999"},{"pid":"ef4479fd89a1f2af074a746cb4b65eea23473781","tid":1474441,"uid":50497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"自推10連倒數"},{"pid":"89f2ad6485a0e61b5b24ab9baaeef887c630a48f","tid":1474441,"uid":50497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"255f308b8953451c10a46a64a3b3de572222c487","tid":1474441,"uid":