7801%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=bdf31d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/500722140081205/posts/1338111096342301?s=611407801&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n如果係藍絲特登搞一個活動扮中立或者黃 使唔使730就已經鋪定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>第二勁撚多藍絲寵主根本唔會參加呢個活動</ins><br />\n講明譴責班死黑警 藍低咁撚撐警點會去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔係藍色唔係撐警先啱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次呢個活動就係要屌鳩班黑警！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>第三本身去光復紅土嘅人都唔會去呢個活動</ins><br />\n小弟身邊諗住去紅土人士當然繼續保衛家園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個活動根本都冇諗住搶光復紅土參加者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目標擺明係打算喺屋企嘆冷氣但又愛護動物/有養寵物嘅和里非<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以大家記住:<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n光復紅土 譴責黑警<br />\n齊齊為動物向催淚彈say no </span></ins><br />\n<br />\n大家睇吓佢哋啲文宣 有乜可能係藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n817咁多活動，你哋同我求其都要參加一個！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FRAo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FRAo1h.jpg&h=3e2e8cc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62xPtsY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62xPtsY.jpg&h=4792fb8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkGphmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkGphmj.jpg&h=c205f0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n83yU70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn83yU70.jpg&h=39fa6bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KOzeEzF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKOzeEzF.jpg&h=dcd02170&s={SIZE